20#include "config.h"

32#include "regs.h"
33#include "insn-attr-common.h" /* for INSN_SCHEDULING. */
34#include "insn-attr.h" /* for init_sched_attrs. */
35#include "run-rtl-passes.h"
36
37/* Run the backend passes, starting at the given pass.
38 Take ownership of INITIAL_PASS_NAME. */
39
40void
41run_rtl_passes (char *initial_pass_name)
42{
43 cfun->pass_startwith = initial_pass_name;
44 max_regno = max_reg_num ();
45
46 /* Pass "expand" normally sets this up. */
47#ifdef INSN_SCHEDULING
48 init_sched_attrs ();
49#endif
50
51 bitmap_obstack_initialize (NULL);
52 bitmap_obstack_initialize (&reg_obstack);
53
54 opt_pass *rest_of_compilation
55 = g->get_passes ()->get_rest_of_compilation ();
56 gcc_assert (rest_of_compilation);
57 execute_pass_list (cfun, rest_of_compilation);
58
59 opt_pass *clean_slate = g->get_passes ()->get_clean_slate ();
60 gcc_assert (clean_slate);
61 execute_pass_list (cfun, clean_slate);
62
63 bitmap_obstack_release (&reg_obstack);
64
65 cfun->curr_properties |= PROP_rtl;
66}
